put it past him.

1122
01:23:50,781 --> 01:23:52,750
[ Sullivan ]
Don't you understand?

1123
01:23:52,750 --> 01:23:55,019
They think I'm dead,
and I'm not dead.

1124
01:23:55,020 --> 01:23:57,022
Well, that's fine.

1125
01:23:57,023 --> 01:23:59,626
Just think what a nice surprise
they'll have when you get out.

1126
01:23:59,626 --> 01:24:03,063
I haven't time
to spend six years.

1127
